Fallujah is an American technical death metal band from San Francisco, They have been around since 2007 and are in the process of reinventing themselves, They have had a series of lineup changes but are in a fully stable and functioning state and have been touring the US since 2009.

Current members

    Alex Hofmann - Studio Guitars, Vocals (2007-present)
    Andrew Baird - Drums (2007-present)
    Scott Carstairs - Guitars (2007-present)
    Rob Morey - Bass (2009-present)
